    {
      "id": "EkCKvG0cnW-kTBynGy39F",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3104.815456886708,
      "y": 1147.8749878742296,
      "width": 670.2395629882812,
      "height": 350,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bWk",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1540792750,
      "version": 494,
      "versionNonce": 2116010226,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782923348421,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "9. Delivery semantics\nExactly once : Idempotency key ( for > 2 retun 429 too many req)\n+Unique Constraint\n+Outbox Pattern\n\nAt least once ( we retry with exp backoff , add in retry queue)\n\n10 consistency between systems\n\ninternal system : exactly once processing\ninternal and PSP : reconciliation and idempotency key ( exactly once)\ndist transaction : SAGA\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "9. Delivery semantics\nExactly once : Idempotency key ( for > 2 retun 429 too many req)\n+Unique Constraint\n+Outbox Pattern\n\nAt least once ( we retry with exp backoff , add in retry queue)\n\n10 consistency between systems\n\ninternal system : exactly once processing\ninternal and PSP : reconciliation and idempotency key ( exactly once)\ndist transaction : SAGA\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "cAuprz8UbUl9TxeDmDVCx",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3996.0638226978035,
      "y": 113.9772903631623,
      "width": 603.1396484375,
      "height": 800,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bWl",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1224958190,
      "version": 135,
      "versionNonce": 1164869422,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782923348421,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "4. Fraud Detection\n\nChecks\n\n\nVelocity\n```\n10 cards\n5 minutes\nSame IP\n```\n\nLocation mismatch\nDevice fingerprint\nBIN lookup\nBlacklist\nRisk score\nOutput\n\n```\nALLOW\nREVIEW\nBLOCK\n```\nFraud detection\nDevice fingerprinting\nIP reputation\nGeolocation mismatch\nVelocity limits (e.g., 20 cards used from one IP in 10 minutes)\nBIN (Bank Identification Number) checks\nBehavioral analysis\nMachine learning risk scoring",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "4. Fraud Detection\n\nChecks\n\n\nVelocity\n```\n10 cards\n5 minutes\nSame IP\n```\n\nLocation mismatch\nDevice fingerprint\nBIN lookup\nBlacklist\nRisk score\nOutput\n\n```\nALLOW\nREVIEW\nBLOCK\n```\nFraud detection\nDevice fingerprinting\nIP reputation\nGeolocation mismatch\nVelocity limits (e.g., 20 cards used from one IP in 10 minutes)\nBIN (Bank Identification Number) checks\nBehavioral analysis\nMachine learning risk scoring",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
