    {
      "id": "sgLc6x_r5yGZV6JVNzCp6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 174,
      "y": 289.5,
      "width": 384.9397888183594,
      "height": 1075,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bWq",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 168681902,
      "version": 783,
      "versionNonce": 192664690,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782992039159,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Clarifications\n\nq. imp features?\nwallet, balance, ledger, transfers\noptional onboarding, kyc, rewards\n\nq. scale?\n1 m tps\n\nq. anything else?\nwe want system to be reconstructable\n\nFunctional req:\nCreate wallet\nview balance\nAdd money\nTransact money internally\nTransfer mney to bank account\nLedger\nOptional\nOnboarding\nKYC\n\nNFR:\n1. Scalable\n2. Reliable\n3. Availablity : 99.9\n4. Any thing finance : consistent\n5. REcorstructible\n\nBack of the envelope calc:\n\n1m tps\nstorage:\n1m tps * 10^5 = 10^11 * 1kb per request\n= 100 tb per day\n1,000,000 tps -> bottelneck DB\n10000 rps = 100 db insteancs\n\ntraffic:\n10 m reads of wallet, balance\n100 k new wallets\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Clarifications\n\nq. imp features?\nwallet, balance, ledger, transfers\noptional onboarding, kyc, rewards\n\nq. scale?\n1 m tps\n\nq. anything else?\nwe want system to be reconstructable\n\nFunctional req:\nCreate wallet\nview balance\nAdd money\nTransact money internally\nTransfer mney to bank account\nLedger\nOptional\nOnboarding\nKYC\n\nNFR:\n1. Scalable\n2. Reliable\n3. Availablity : 99.9\n4. Any thing finance : consistent\n5. REcorstructible\n\nBack of the envelope calc:\n\n1m tps\nstorage:\n1m tps * 10^5 = 10^11 * 1kb per request\n= 100 tb per day\n1,000,000 tps -> bottelneck DB\n10000 rps = 100 db insteancs\n\ntraffic:\n10 m reads of wallet, balance\n100 k new wallets\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
