    {
      "id": "dVhCiX6Nn8Wqtzvilj7vk",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1936.8142258226583,
      "y": 1115.6380300426085,
      "width": 1179.6190185546875,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bY8",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1840382958,
      "version": 164,
      "versionNonce": 1572249390,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782992039159,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Use Event driven archietctire and event sourcing with commands, events, states and state machines for reproduceability\n\nUse CQRS : to serve the load better",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Use Event driven archietctire and event sourcing with commands, events, states and state machines for reproduceability\n\nUse CQRS : to serve the load better",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "quB2lfxndC6A9Onh51mgx",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3474.9979513372186,
      "y": 358.2153251955437,
      "width": 516.1996459960938,
      "height": 900,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "dashed",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bY9",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 156546862,
      "version": 648,
      "versionNonce": 1978184370,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782992039159,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Scalability and Availability\nMulti regio deployments and multi Az\nEKS -> aut scalaing\nDB : replication,  partitioning and sharding by userId\nUse ques for loose coupling and availability\nuse DLQs\n\n\n2. Resiliency\nMonitoring and laerting\n\n3. Ensure no double booking\nidempotency key\nlocks where needed,\npessimistic : SELCT for updates\noptimistic : preferred\nversion_num\n\n4. Dist transaction\n2PC\nTC/C\nSAGA - preferred\n\nsecurity\n\nevesdropping : HTTPs\nman in middle attach : TLS everytwhere. mTLS\nddos : rate limiter\nencrption\nno PII writes\nPCI compliant\nstep up auth\nAuthentication : OAuth/JWT\nuse card tokenization\nHSM for private keys store\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Scalability and Availability\nMulti regio deployments and multi Az\nEKS -> aut scalaing\nDB : replication,  partitioning and sharding by userId\nUse ques for loose coupling and availability\nuse DLQs\n\n\n2. Resiliency\nMonitoring and laerting\n\n3. Ensure no double booking\nidempotency key\nlocks where needed,\npessimistic : SELCT for updates\noptimistic : preferred\nversion_num\n\n4. Dist transaction\n2PC\nTC/C\nSAGA - preferred\n\nsecurity\n\nevesdropping : HTTPs\nman in middle attach : TLS everytwhere. mTLS\nddos : rate limiter\nencrption\nno PII writes\nPCI compliant\nstep up auth\nAuthentication : OAuth/JWT\nuse card tokenization\nHSM for private keys store\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
