    {
      "id": "S3YPT_TdKrqbi31k9b6wX",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 236,
      "y": 214.5,
      "width": 506.57958984375,
      "height": 1350,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bYI",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1207948210,
      "version": 869,
      "versionNonce": 1664439986,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783006000259,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Req:\n\nq. broker or stock exchange?\nstock exchange\n\nq. imp features\ncreate order \nview order\nview stocks and prices\nmatch buy and sell orders\n\nq. order types?\nlimit and market order\n\nq. only stocks or derivatives as well??\nonly stocks\n\nq. number of tickers?\n1000\n\nq. scale?\n1 billion oorder per day\n\nq. after hours settlements?\nno\n\nFunctional req:\ncreate order ( buy or sell)\nwith either limit or market order\nview historical orders\nview stocks and prices\nStock exchange match buy and sell orders\ncommunication: FIX :Financial Information eXchange)\nand APIs\n\nNFR:\nCorrectness > Availability\nScalability\nDuarability : 11 9s\nAvailability : 99.99\nlow latency : < 10 ms\n\nBack of the envelope calc:\n\n1 billion orders per day\nin normal case\n10^9 / 10^5 = 10000\ntrading window is 9:30 to 4 pm\n6:30 hours\n10^9 / 6.5 * 3600 \n= 10^7 / 6.5 * 36 = 240\n= 10^7 / 240\n= 1000 * 10^4 / 240\n= 42,000 transactions per sec",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Req:\n\nq. broker or stock exchange?\nstock exchange\n\nq. imp features\ncreate order \nview order\nview stocks and prices\nmatch buy and sell orders\n\nq. order types?\nlimit and market order\n\nq. only stocks or derivatives as well??\nonly stocks\n\nq. number of tickers?\n1000\n\nq. scale?\n1 billion oorder per day\n\nq. after hours settlements?\nno\n\nFunctional req:\ncreate order ( buy or sell)\nwith either limit or market order\nview historical orders\nview stocks and prices\nStock exchange match buy and sell orders\ncommunication: FIX :Financial Information eXchange)\nand APIs\n\nNFR:\nCorrectness > Availability\nScalability\nDuarability : 11 9s\nAvailability : 99.99\nlow latency : < 10 ms\n\nBack of the envelope calc:\n\n1 billion orders per day\nin normal case\n10^9 / 10^5 = 10000\ntrading window is 9:30 to 4 pm\n6:30 hours\n10^9 / 6.5 * 3600 \n= 10^7 / 6.5 * 36 = 240\n= 10^7 / 240\n= 1000 * 10^4 / 240\n= 42,000 transactions per sec",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
