    {
      "id": "B4wmOhAkpfrMU_tyI4w46",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2905.169001438878,
      "y": 1469.9370912782,
      "width": 1304.0391845703125,
      "height": 275,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bZt",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1327427246,
      "version": 424,
      "versionNonce": 1632124210,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783006000260,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Event sourcing : commands, events and states\n\nImprove availability: Keep multiple servers running ( blue-green) and consuming data on the basis of mmmap, but not publishing matches\n\nif both servers die, \n    mmap -> replicated via RPC t another AZ\n    elect leader via raft\n\nLatency:\n    above helps reduce the latency to 10ms\n    but we need to cotrol for JVM GC pause and optimise it, use shenandoah or ZGc",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Event sourcing : commands, events and states\n\nImprove availability: Keep multiple servers running ( blue-green) and consuming data on the basis of mmmap, but not publishing matches\n\nif both servers die, \n    mmap -> replicated via RPC t another AZ\n    elect leader via raft\n\nLatency:\n    above helps reduce the latency to 10ms\n    but we need to cotrol for JVM GC pause and optimise it, use shenandoah or ZGc",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "E78zdc59afnLWBz_F4gcE",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 918.3943965697977,
      "y": 1931.41738662559,
      "width": 138.1999053955078,
      "height": 200,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
