    {
      "id": "CrXvmHYmxau25bpaDPkdQ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 227,
      "y": 218.5,
      "width": 380.19970703125,
      "height": 1050,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "ba5",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 429159598,
      "version": 509,
      "versionNonce": 506104174,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783233129479,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Req:\n\nq. what are types of fraud?\nAccount takeover\nCard theft\nIdentity theft\nPromo and referral abuse\nLoan fraud\nMoney laundering\nAuthorized Push Payment (APP) Fraud\n\nq. scale\n10k TPS\n\nq. latency\n<100 ms\n\nq. ML models for different systems?\nyes\n\nq. what to do when fraud is detected?\nApprove, reject, verify by human\n\nFunctional req:\nDetect frauds in real time:\nAccount takeover\nCard theft\nIdentity theft\nPromo and referral abuse\nLoan fraud\nMoney laundering\nAuthorized Push Payment (APP) Fraud\n\nNFR:\nAvailable 99.99\nlow latency\nlow false positives\n\nback of the envelope calc\n\ntraffic : 10k tps \nstorage : 10k * 1kb * 84600 * 365",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Req:\n\nq. what are types of fraud?\nAccount takeover\nCard theft\nIdentity theft\nPromo and referral abuse\nLoan fraud\nMoney laundering\nAuthorized Push Payment (APP) Fraud\n\nq. scale\n10k TPS\n\nq. latency\n<100 ms\n\nq. ML models for different systems?\nyes\n\nq. what to do when fraud is detected?\nApprove, reject, verify by human\n\nFunctional req:\nDetect frauds in real time:\nAccount takeover\nCard theft\nIdentity theft\nPromo and referral abuse\nLoan fraud\nMoney laundering\nAuthorized Push Payment (APP) Fraud\n\nNFR:\nAvailable 99.99\nlow latency\nlow false positives\n\nback of the envelope calc\n\ntraffic : 10k tps \nstorage : 10k * 1kb * 84600 * 365",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
