      "updated": 1783233129479,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Seperate model for \neach use case\n\ncreate a score of\n0 to 1\n0 being safe and\n1 being risky\n\nbased on factors liek\n\npayments / cards\ngelocation\nnumber of payments in last n mins\ntarnsaction trend\nblacklist\n\nkyc\nblacklist, \nid match\n\nloans\nid match",
